thread.title: Sharon and Michelle
thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Sharon and Michelle

author: Sharon and Michelle
title: Sharon and Michelle
text:
Great price, great car, made our holiday so much more as opposed to using public transport.
First time users of a GPS, made driving in and around Auckland easy and we are from Palmerston North.
Would definitely use again and recommend to anyone.
Thank you Omega.
